  <chunk id="99fbfb118e293a937583b9338256f9d216cf8c5e.c3" text="I am generally supportive of this manuscript. Although the SREBP/FAS pathways have been implicated as both virally manipulated and a broad-spectrum drug target in previous studies, the identification of a bioactive lipid inhibitor with efficacy in vitro and in vivo plus a good selectivity index is quite interesting. Some experiments lack controls and many are over-interpreted. This needs to be addressed in revision. Specific points:">
